item.description: [...] It was the Sunday after Thanksgiving and Cindy and Paul had an early morning flight out from Seattle on Monday. They had done well – Thanksgiving dinner Thursday, Kwanjai and soiree at Rosemarie’s on Friday, kickass pot-luck on Saturday (and Mt. Si hike) and a nice little pub dinner at Bick’s that very evening. [...]
